## Project Overview

| Aspect | Details |
|--------|---------|
| Language | Visual FoxPro 9.0 |
| Database | SQL Server [VERSION] |
| Architecture | SQL Pass-Through (SPT) with buffered cursors |

```
YourProject/
├── Prgs/           # Source code (.prg)
├── Forms/          # Forms (.scx or .sc2 for version control)
├── Classes/        # Class libraries (.vcx or .vc2)
├── Reports/        # Reports (.frx)
├── Logs/           # Application logs
