## Database Field Naming Conventions

| Prefix | SQL Type | VFP Type | Rule |
|--------|----------|----------|------|
| `id*` | INT IDENTITY/INT | Integer | IDENTITY=PK, INT=FK |
| `d*` | **DATE** | Date | Use `Date()` NOT `Datetime()`! |
| `t*` | DATETIME | DateTime | Use `Datetime()` |
| `n*` | NUMERIC | Numeric | Numbers |
| `c*` | VARCHAR/CHAR | Character | Strings |
| `l*` | BIT | Logical | Booleans |

---

## Variable Prefixes

| Prefix | Scope |
|--------|-------|
| `gl_*` | Global (PUBLIC) |
| `m.*` | Memory variables (SCATTER) |
| `lc*`, `ln*`, `ld*`, `ll*` | Local (char, numeric, date, logical) |
| `lo*` | Local Object |
| `la*` | Local Array |

