## Key Functions

```foxpro
*-- SQL Execution (customize for your project)
sql_exec_safe("SELECT ...", "cursor")

*-- Open table with buffering
foloseste("tablename", "cursor")

*-- Save buffered changes
sql_tableupdate("cursor")

*-- Close cursor (auto-saves)
inchide("cursor")

*-- Logging
log_error("message")
log_info("message")
```

---

## Code Rules

### Rule 1: Date() vs Datetime()
```foxpro
*-- d* fields (DATE) -> Date()
m.dbirthdate = Date()

*-- t* fields (DATETIME) -> Datetime()
m.tcreated = Datetime()
```

### Rule 2: No ELSEIF in VFP
```foxpro
*-- WRONG
IF x > 10
    y = 1
ELSEIF x > 5   && VFP has no ELSEIF!
    y = 2
ENDIF

*-- CORRECT
DO CASE
CASE x > 10
    y = 1
CASE x > 5
    y = 2
ENDCASE
```

### Rule 3: SCATTER/REPLACE (Not GATHER!)
```foxpro
*-- Read with Scatter
SCATTER MEMVAR

*-- Write specific fields with REPLACE
REPLACE cname WITH m.cname IN cursor
sql_tableupdate("cursor")
```

### Rule 4: NULL Handling
```foxpro
*-- Always check type before comparing dates
IF VARTYPE(ddeadline) = 'D' AND ddeadline < DATE()
    *-- Overdue
ENDIF
```

