## Common Errors

| Error | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| "Conversion failed date/time" | Use `Date()` for d* fields |
| "Unrecognized command verb" | Replace ELSEIF with DO CASE |
| Error 1492 "No key columns" | Check cursor KeyFieldList property |

